project description:
a live website for cricket score 
we have 4 pages:
1. setup page:
setup.html , setup.css , setup.js
2. live page:
live.html , live.css , live.js
3. score page:
score.html , score.css , score.js
4. summary page:
summary.html , summary.css , summary.js

To run the project:
open setup.html in browser(chrome).
